divs: Sighting DetailsI came across the field into the yard and observed when exiting my car two large yellow blinking lights low in the sky which I thought were attached to a laarge oval object. I entered the house and reached for my binoculars and the object vanished. ON February 11th two lights were observed steady in the sky some distant away and one disappeared while the other stayed. At another time (all in the western sky) two lights were so close, I thought the trees were on fire--in the year 2010.sss
Summary: appeared large dish with two large yellow lights then vanished
